726392f-a.title: Queens: Cooper Avenue - 75th Street
726392f-a.text:
Cooper Ave., south side, between 75th Street (left) and 76th
Street (right), showing John Schmidts' house which was erected about
1885. The Long Island Railroad has a riht of way behind this
property.
May 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
